end;

(*
RandomLeft
~~~~~~~~~~
> function RandomLeft(Lo, Hi: Double): Double;
> function RandomLeft(Lo, Hi: Int64): Int64;

Generates a random number between `Lo` and `Hi` weighted towards `Lo`
*)
