GaussRand
~~~~~~~~~
> function GaussRand(Mean, Dev: Double): Double

Generates a random gaussian/normal number.
*)
procedure _LapeGaussRand(const Params: PParamArray; const Result: Pointer); LAPE_WRAPPER_CALLING_CONV
begin
